{"tid":602640,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友想點？","createTime":"2018-03-23T06:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T01:44:56.000Z","uid":94094,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"eb6c0332c9dbadb6ba5247e5040a5e317f6b1621","tid":602640,"uid":94094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T06:35:16.000Z","msg":"琴日同男朋友去咗旺角行街<br />\n佢問正間食咩好<br />\n我諗咗一陣答佢 食譚仔好冇<br />\n之後佢吓咗我一句 話特燈出嚟就食譚仔？<br />\n咁我問返佢 咁你想食咩啊？<br />\n佢又笑笑口話冇所謂<br />\n到行到間野門口 我望一望佢<br />\n心知都有啲野<br />\n入到去嗌野食 佢就咩都唔叫<br />\n成程就篤電話同黑晒面<br />\n食完出返去問佢做咩<br />\n佢話一早講咗唔鍾意食 又逼佢食。<br />\n<br />\n其實你想食咩咪直接講....<br />\n使唔使到而家都仲嬲緊...."},{"pid":"2de95045fad36fec36e31fc69526a479c6e9b61e","tid":602640,"uid":26845,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T06:36:12.000Z","msg":"互射番咪冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e272a9e930390dadac9de3af9b685797183053","tid":602640,"uid":57835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T06:37:04.000Z","msg":"你調撚轉佢有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597c4bcf1b12c35e1fbd48ff98a5137e328b2a09","tid":602640,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T06:38:10.000Z","msg":"佢想食你條腸姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d51055a1b177ac3891dc857529d496055c145c9","tid":602640,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T06:38:40.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4daa82aba01d9c66b04a7b71db3ce413dc8888a4","tid":602640,"uid":147743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T06:41:39.000Z","msg":"成個女人咁，未試過同男朋友因爲食野而嘈交<br />\n因為我同佢好多野都岩食<br />\n自己唔鐘意食又唔講，要你睇穿佢個心<br />\n你都係多啲留意佢啲表情啦"},{"pid":"c2ba1151bc45528a9bc24614d